Listing information is from various brokers who participate in the Bright MLS IDX program and not all listings may be visible on the site. 
The property information being provided on or through the website is for the personal, non-commercial use of consumers and such information may not be used for any purpose other than to identify prospective properties consumers may be interested in purchasing.

Property information displayed is deemed reliable but is not guaranteed.

data.description: Welcome home! This gorgeous Baltimore County townhome is a must see! You'll love the updated kitchen with granite counters and stainless steel appliances. The living room features an amazing built in fireplace . The living  and dining room  are equipped with finished hardwood floors. There is also a nicely finished deck in the backyard perfect for entertaining. The finished basement with 1/2 bath and laundry provides an additional space to gather with guests.  Roof was replaced in 2019. Schedule your showing today!
